reviewText: Great lesbian stand up comic in the business.
if I were to just say that this woman is hilarious that would be a understatement....she literally had me crying with laughter!

I saw her on OUT TV, didn't know what to expect, especially that I've seen so many stand up comedians, but I ended up enjoying it a lot and this is the 3rd DVD I buy on here, bought two others as gifts and both of my friends loved her...
